metadata.name: Born Hero
metadata.description:
BORN HERO
Edition 1 of 1

This artwork is personal, communal and natural consisting of figures reminiscent narrative of identity mortality loss hate and love.

The artwork also deploys obsession of hard work, success and perfection. 

Hardwork will never betray you!

Dimension: 5000px x 6668px
Type: PNG
Dpi: 800
